Achievements.Name: Reinforcement
Achievements.Description: Earned by assisting teammates kill 100 enemy players.

Achievements.Name: CarBoom!
Achievements.Description: Earned by killing an opponent in a vehicle with a grenade.

Achievements.Name: Drive-by
Achievements.Description: Earned by killing 50 opposing players as a passenger in a vehicle.

Achievements.Name: Right of Way
Achievements.Description: Earned by killing 500 players with a vehicle.

Achievements.Name: R&R
Achievements.Description: Earned by regenerating enough health to have healed you 99 times.

Achievements.Name: MVP
Achievements.Description: Earned by achieving the MVP status at the end of a match 5 times total.

Achievements.Name: Criminal Mastermind
Achievements.Description: Earned by successfully completing 100 missions as a Criminal.

Achievements.Name: Equalizer
Achievements.Description: Earned by successfully completing 100 missions as an Enforcer.

Achievements.Name: Medal Chaser
Achievements.Description: Earned by winning 100 positive medals in opposed missions.

Achievements.Name: Carbeque
Achievements.Description: Earned by destroying 100 vehicles while the driver is at the wheel.

Achievements.Name: Seasoned Veteran
Achievements.Description: Earned by spending a full day of game time opposed to enemy players.
